data.description: Welcome to 89 Alder Landing, a meticulously maintained 2018-built home nestled on a tranquil cul-de-sac street. This exquisite property boasts a private, fenced-in backyard with picturesque views and meticulously landscaped grounds, creating an idyllic setting for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, and entertaining. The main floor features a spacious kitchen adorned with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a generous island overlooking the family room, alongside a living/family room and a versatile formal dining room/office. Upstairs, an oversized master suite awaits with a substantial walk-in closet and luxurious leather granite dual vanities, accompanied by three more well-appointed bedrooms and a secondary full bathroom. Enjoy the added peace of mind with this Artisan Built home, complete with the assurance of a New Home Build Warranty, which still has four years remaining. Beyond the home's charms, the Seven Hills community offers an array of amenities, including a clubhouse, an oversized pool with a thrilling super waterslide, a zero-entry kids' pool with a splash pad, tennis, volleyball, and pickleball courts, expansive green spaces, and golf cart paths that wind throughout the community. Additionally, extensive walking trails connect with Pumpkinvine Creek Nature Park, a sprawling 110-acre reserve featuring biking and hiking trails. Don't miss the opportunity to introduce your buyers to this exceptional property, as it promises to exceed expectations.
